{"word":"ὄρυγμα","slug":"ὄρυγμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὄρυγμα</b></el> <el>(ὄρυγμα, ατος, τό,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ὀρύσσω'><el>ὀρύσσω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a trench, ditch, moat</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>scrobs</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>: <i>a tunnel, mine</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>: —<el>ὄρ. τύμβου</el> the grave, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>= <a href='S:ὄρυξις'><el>ὄρυξις</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}